## 3. 总体架构图

### 3.1 分层架构（Mermaid）

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "用户交互层 [Presentation]"
        CLI[CLI Interface<br/>REPL / Stream Renderer]
        UI_FLAGS[Config & Flags<br/>--model --trust --verbose]
    end

    subgraph "Agent 编排层 [Orchestration]"
        ORCH[Agent Orchestrator<br/>ReAct Loop / Plan & Execute]
        PLAN[Task Planner<br/>Decomposition / Priority]
        ROUTER[Tool Router<br/>Selection & Dispatch]
    end

    subgraph "LLM 抽象层 [LLM Gateway]"
        LLM_API[LLM API Client<br/>Claude / OpenAI / Local]
        PROMPT[Prompt Builder<br/>System / Context / Tools Schema]
        CACHE[Cache Manager<br/>Prompt Caching / Response Cache]
        TOKEN[Token Counter<br/>Budget Allocation]
    end

    subgraph "工具执行层 [Tool Execution]"
        TOOL_REG[Tool Registry<br/>Discovery & Validation]
        TOOL_EXEC[Tool Executor<br/>Dispatch / Timeout / Retry]
        TOOLS[Tool Implementations<br/>ReadFile / EditFile / Shell / Grep / Glob ...]
    end

    subgraph "文件/代码操作层 [File Operations]"
        FILE_RW[File Reader/Writer<br/>Read / Write / Search-Replace]
        DIFF[Diff Engine<br/>Generate / Apply / Validate]
        VCS[Git Integration<br/>Status / Diff / Commit / Branch]
    end

    subgraph "上下文与记忆层 [Context & Memory]"
        CTX[Context Manager<br/>Window Management / Compression]
        RETRIEVE[Code Retriever<br/>Semantic Search / AST Index]
        MEM[Memory Store<br/>Project Knowledge / User Prefs]
    end

    subgraph "沙箱/权限控制层 [Security]"
        PERM[Permission Manager<br/>Trust Levels / ACL]
        SANDBOX[Sandbox Executor<br/>Docker / nsjail / macOS Seatbelt]
        AUDIT[Audit Logger<br/>All Tool Calls / File Changes]
    end

    subgraph "状态与可观测层 [State & Observability]"
        STATE[State Manager<br/>Session Persistence / Checkpoint]
        TRACE[Trace Collector<br/>OpenTelemetry / Structured Log]
        EVAL[Evaluation Framework<br/>Success Rate / Cost / Latency]
    end

    CLI --> ORCH
    UI_FLAGS --> ORCH
    ORCH --> PLAN
    ORCH --> ROUTER
    ORCH --> LLM_API
    ROUTER --> TOOL_REG
    TOOL_REG --> TOOL_EXEC
    TOOL_EXEC --> TOOLS
    TOOLS --> FILE_RW
    TOOLS --> SANDBOX
    FILE_RW --> DIFF
    FILE_RW --> VCS
    ORCH --> CTX
    CTX --> RETRIEVE
    CTX --> MEM
    LLM_API --> PROMPT
    LLM_API --> CACHE
    LLM_API --> TOKEN
    PERM --> SANDBOX
    PERM --> TOOL_EXEC
    STATE --> ORCH
    TRACE --> ORCH
    TRACE --> TOOL_EXEC
    EVAL --> TRACE
    AUDIT --> TOOL_EXEC
    AUDIT --> FILE_RW
```

### 3.2 核心循环流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant CLI as CLI Interface
    participant ORCH as Orchestrator
    participant LLM as LLM Gateway
    participant CTX as Context Manager
    participant TOOL as Tool Executor
    participant SEC as Security Layer
    participant FS as File System
    participant LOG as Observability

    U->>CLI: 输入指令
    CLI->>ORCH: user_message(instruction)
    ORCH->>CTX: build_messages(instruction)
    CTX-->>ORCH: messages[]

    loop ReAct Loop (max N turns)
        ORCH->>LLM: stream_chat(messages, tools)
        LLM-->>ORCH: stream_response (text + tool_calls)
        ORCH->>CLI: stream_text_to_user(text)

        alt LLM 请求调用工具
            ORCH->>SEC: check_permission(tool_call)
            alt 权限允许
                SEC-->>ORCH: approved
            else 需要确认
                SEC->>CLI: prompt_user_confirmation(tool_call)
                CLI->>SEC: user_decision
                SEC-->>ORCH: approved/denied
            end

            alt approved
                ORCH->>TOOL: execute(tool_call)
                TOOL->>FS: perform_operation
                FS-->>TOOL: result
                TOOL-->>ORCH: tool_result
                ORCH->>CTX: append_assistant_and_tool_result
                ORCH->>LOG: trace(tool_call, result, tokens, latency)
            else denied
                ORCH->>CTX: append_permission_denied
            end
        else LLM 输出纯文本（无工具调用）
            ORCH-->>CLI: final_response
        end
    end

    CLI-->>U: 显示最终结果
    ORCH->>LOG: log_session_summary(tokens, cost, duration)
```

